<item>
            <title>[HBASE-553] Remove bloom filters from HBase when they become available in Hadoop</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-553</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hadoop is incorporating the bloom filter code that is in HBase to make a BloomFilterMapFile (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-3063&quot; title=&quot;BloomMapFile - fail-fast version of MapFile for sparsely populated key space&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HADOOP-3063&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HADOOP-3063&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;). Once this is committed to Hadoop trunk, the bloom filter code can be removed from HBase.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12392647">HBASE-553</key>
            <summary>Remove bloom filters from HBase when they become available in Hadoop</summary>
